hmm yeah that didn't work out so good last time... 

yesterday's weigh in though... 257.6.

down another .6
current weight- 255.4
total loss- 12.4

Week 2 weigh in -8.8
current weight- 259

hooray for the 250's again! i've missed you.

down to 31 points a day.

starting over. first week of 2008. first meeting of 2008. i'm DIGUSTED with myself. 267, almost 268. i worked too hard to get down to just let  myself gain back ALL that weight. im determined to get back on track and get back to 230 as a first goal. that where i was when i started back sliding. 

first MINI MINI goal though, is get into the 250's. i panic less for some reason once i dont see 260's. haha. whatever.

OK! i created this journal, just to keep track of my weight loss. After quitting meetings and doing it on my own now, I'm going to try and use this journal and my communities more! (my old journal has friends who i don't think need to see this stuff)

This mornings weight was 257.5. 

Got up and went to Curves like I'm supposed to! Good start. I CAN do this.
